                <h4>Company Background</h4>
                <p>
                    @OrgName (@OrgInitials), is a HR services firm, Javed Arif, the Chief Executive of the firm, has been a Marketing & Sales senior Executive since 1974 and carrying HR practitioner experience since 2002. His local and International exposure enabled @OrgInitials  to become one of the trusted name in  the Human Capital Management Sector.
                    The firm is committed to the principles which have always been the hallmark of our practice by safeguarding the integrity of a thorough search process, respecting the value and importance of confidentiality, honoring the trust that our clients place in us, treating every prospective candidate with dignity and adhering to the highest ethical standards. We are committed in providing exemplary HR consultancy and executive recruitment services to our clients.
